{"word":"G1625 - ἐκτρέφω - ektréphō - ek-tref'-o - Bring up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκτρέφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ektréphō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-tref'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போஷி, வளர்"},{"paragraph":"1. to nourish up to maturity"},{"paragraph":"2. to nurture, bring up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G5142 - τρέφω - tréphō - tref'-o/5142\">G5142</a>; to <i>rear up</i> to maturity, that is, (generally) to <i>cherish</i> or <i>train:</i> - bring up, nourish.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}